<div class=main>
<section class="intro">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="intro__title">How to Use Project Management System</h1>
        <p class="intro__text">
            Our project management system is designed to help you manage your
            projects more efficiently, collaborate with your team, and track your
            progress. Here are some tips on how to use our system:
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="features">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="features__title">1. Create Projects and Tasks</h2>
        <p class="features__text">
            To get started, create a new project and break it down into smaller
            tasks. This will help you stay organized and on track.
        </p>

        <h2 class="features__title">2. Assign Tasks to Team Members</h2>
        <p class="features__text">
            Assign tasks to your team members and set deadlines. This will help
            ensure that everyone knows what they need to do and when they need to
            do it by.
        </p>

        <h2 class="features__title">3. Collaborate and Communicate</h2>
        <p class="features__text">
            Use our system's collaboration tools to communicate with your team and
            share files and information. This will help ensure that everyone is on
            the same page and working towards the same goal.
        </p>

        <h2 class="features__title">4. Monitor Progress and Make Adjustments</h2>
        <p class="features__text">
            Use our system's progress tracking tools to monitor the progress of
            your projects and tasks. Make adjustments as needed to ensure that
            you're staying on track and meeting your goals.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <div class="container">
        <p>&copy; 2023 Project Management System</p>
    </div>
</footer>
</div>

